      <title>沙特矿业部长认为在加拿大进行交易没有障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/saudi-s-mining-minister-sees-no-obstacles-to-dealmaking-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管沙特阿拉伯政府规定限制国有外国实体的投资，但沙特阿拉伯矿业部长并不认为有任何障碍阻止该国与加拿大采矿业进行交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/saudi-s-mining-minister-sees-no-obstacles-to-dealmaking-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:29:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
