      <title>印度批准采取措施遏制股票衍生品交易热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/india-clears-steps-to-curb-trading-rush-in-stock-derivatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于散户参与度不断提高，投机性赌注达到全球最高水平，印度证券监管机构周二宣布采取措施限制该国股票衍生品交易的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/india-clears-steps-to-curb-trading-rush-in-stock-derivatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行称欧盟需要更大的银行，首席执行官瞄准德国商业银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/unicredit-ceo-says-eu-needs-bigger-banks-as-he-eyes-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔（Andrea Orcel）正在寻求收购德国竞争对手德国商业银行（Commerzbank AG）。他表示，欧洲的银行规模不足以满足欧盟的融资需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/unicredit-ceo-says-eu-needs-bigger-banks-as-he-eyes-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国千亿美元交易激增，欧洲其他国家落后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/germany-s-100-billion-deal-surge-leaves-rest-of-europe-behind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去几周，德国出现了一系列巨额收购交易，交易额已接近 1000 亿美元，增幅超过欧洲其他地区，让银行家们对今年剩余时间的复苏充满希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/germany-s-100-billion-deal-surge-leaves-rest-of-europe-behind</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
